::Orchestra::

     Orchestra grinned.

      "Ah, please, take me to your leader, I'm awaiting to join you," He
said, smiling.

       He went to walk over, but then he fell onto his knees.  He got up,
wiping dirt off him.

         "Uh, I had a rough landing," He muttered, not really to
Blacknightmare, but not to himself either.
